longBusinessSummary: Doro AB (publ), a technology company, develops telecom and technology products and services for seniors and individuals with special needs. The company offers smartphones, hemma doorbell, watch, and tablet under the Doro brand. It operates in Nordic, West and South Europe, Africa, Central- and Eastern Europe, the United Kingdom, Ireland, and internationally. Doro AB (publ) was incorporated in 1972 and is headquartered in Malmö, Sweden.
